<L>__{exterior washington square day}
<A>__{jacob and michael walk through washington square park.}
<C>__{jacob}
<D>__{it was paradise, michael. you showed it to me. you were there.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{well that's good to know.}
<C>__{jacob}
<D>__{mike, it was real. it was glorious.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{glorious. i'm not surprised. i fed you enough of that stuff to send a horse to heaven. i'm just glad you came back.}
